# Code Comments in English

All code comments, JSDoc blocks, and inline documentation must be written in **English**.

## Applies to

- JSDoc (`/** ... */`, `@param`, `@returns`, etc.)
- Block comments (`/* ... */`)
- Inline comments (`// ...`)
- README and technical documentation

## Does not apply to

- User-facing strings (UI labels, aria-label, error messages shown to users)
- Content that must match the app's display language (e.g. Polish for bacatel.pl)

## Example

```javascript
// ✅ GOOD
/** Returns the currently active theme (saved or from system preference). */

// ❌ BAD
/** Zwraca aktualnie aktywny motyw (zapamiętany lub z preferencji systemu). */
```
